{"tid":2072760,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝醒突然好似卑雷打左一下落黎","createTime":"2020-06-20T21:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T05:06:08.000Z","uid":79771,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22d471567b488ffbad4f222909672439c9584e20","tid":2072760,"uid":79771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T21:43:31.000Z","msg":"突然有個想法- 去考警察<br />\n我唔知有咩原因會咁諗<br />\n<br />\n無返工做左幾年廢青<br />\n讀十幾年書，考個保安牌未返過工<br />\n日日係咁不斷沉輪<br />\n身邊越黎越少朋友<br />\n結婚既結婚<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知而家可以做咩<br />\n繼續沉輪落去 等家人仙遊果時 就係訓街之時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172f49df1897332095db3ee8ceddcdfc0bcdcb6e","tid":2072760,"uid":79771,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T21:48:40.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮唔講野 <br />\n<br />\n呢個敏感時期講警察都係卑人形容黑警多<br />\n<br />\n我都唔做咩突然會咁諗<br />\n<br />\n首先自己體能唔得"},{"pid":"6e2283cfaee15a25e502051833621c614dd5e7d5","tid":2072760,"uid":162268,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T21:49:27.000Z","msg":"想做就做<br />\n唔洗理其他人點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712b3b62bcf1d2f9c28298d0bd799aa6d27bee63","tid":2072760,"uid":302149,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T21:51:23.000Z","msg":"你無嘢吖嘛？紀律部隊有消防海關懲戒唔考<br />\n你有人唔做，走去做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span></span>，犀利啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8f6ab306ddfa46e65f9743956ef5cb1d42d0b0","tid":2072760,"uid":265932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T21:51:37.000Z","msg":"好吖，有想法係好事。<br />\n我都做咗年幾廢青，今朝起身突然間想去做太空人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00817ab4b47bacc68cfcb415a5fca58c2c87ca4d","tid":2072760,"uid":79771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"712b3b62bcf1d2f9c28298d0bd799aa6d27bee63","tid":2072760,"uid":302149,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"